---
title: Double Sweet Soy Beef & Pumpkin Nourish Bowl with Celery Slaw & Roasted Carrot
description: If pumpkin is on the menu then fire up that oven and get ready for a delicious dinner. Sweet and soy beef strips in a rich sauce
will be the perfect accompaniment to the vibrant veggies. If that wasn't enough to quip your interest, there’s even a sprinkling of
sesame seeds in the mix.
